WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.280 --> 00:00:03.520
I only copied it twice last night.

2
00:00:03.700 --> 00:00:04.800
Why are there a few more of Mom's handwriting?

3
00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:05.860
Mom's extra handwriting?

4
00:00:06.420 --> 00:00:07.320
Could it be Huo Jiuling helped

5
00:00:07.320 --> 00:00:09.120
me copy? Impossible,

6
00:00:09.140 --> 00:00:10.800
impossible. He's a gangster

7
00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:11.900
rolling up his sleeves

8
00:00:11.900 --> 00:00:15.080
to help me copy books? Forget it,

9
00:00:15.080 --> 00:00:16.360
forget it, let's go quickly,

10
00:00:16.740 --> 00:00:17.720
I'm going to be late for class.

11
00:00:27.720 --> 00:00:29.640
Aren't you busy today?

12
00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:32.200
When am I not busy?

13
00:00:33.760 --> 00:00:36.200
Then why did you send me to school?

14
00:00:39.120 --> 00:00:41.260
What do you think?

15
00:00:43.100 --> 00:00:45.520
Afraid I'll run off again?

16
00:00:47.140 --> 00:00:47.720
Dare you?

17
00:00:50.680 --> 00:00:54.120
You helped me copy my lessons yesterday.

18
00:00:55.140 --> 00:00:57.120
Suddenly I feel like...

19
00:00:58.260 --> 00:00:58.800
Why?

20
00:00:59.880 --> 00:01:01.800
Am I not being obvious enough?

21
00:01:03.120 --> 00:01:03.900
It's good.

22
00:01:04.680 --> 00:01:06.680
You're the first woman in my life,

23
00:01:06.680 --> 00:01:07.820
and you'll be my last

24
00:01:07.820 --> 00:01:09.010
woman. Understand?

25
00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:14.320
Actually... I don't quite understand.

